Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽的  早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是絕讚的中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦  賞雪溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我沖熱水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜小夜  堆雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進浴池裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙  好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快鎮靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極樂極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完星星之後果然還是要這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過附近居然有這麼好的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  雖然旅館裡的澡堂也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是開放感就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了如果不好好泡一下要死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天結果還是變成了遊戲大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為黎明的時候天氣才好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要回去了  只好賭一下今晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天其實也沒怎麼看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  我們也做了一樣的事  不能只顧著說別人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一年級的夏季合宿吧  三波為了買堅果擅自外出…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了去找她和她一起被困在霧中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是只有我們兩人的夏日的山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.37,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:40.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}當時的部長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當時學姐們也是發射了波動炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到江戶川同學點閃光燈才想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一年的  天氣一直不好  所以就對著雲打著玩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊談論著萌的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想來  我們現在所走的路就是從那時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波動炮…就作為我們高見女中天文部的傳統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…只是隨便想出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小蓬蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是必須要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方商店也都是很遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜不穿衣服顯得更豐滿  真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且皮膚光滑得像雞蛋一樣  可以讓我摸摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是說  已經在摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係  有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小星見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和想的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個  小蓬蓬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們…她們絕對是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是在引誘我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此偷看吧…就去偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她們這樣  就去偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說別露出身體啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  草哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們那邊浴池怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後洗了嗎  毛巾有拿過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  美星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生不要偷窺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  江戶川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要攔著我  大八木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要連肩膀都泡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是糟透了  真的完了  絕對完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習用腦之後要補充糖份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  路萬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.70,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總整理  檢查  讀了這本書就能及格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  很適合現在的總複習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能多陪陪我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是準備考試的學生  就算吃頓飯也沒什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說已經預約好飯店了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是近江小姐的預約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是我經常和家人一起來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要點些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥膳湯和香粥…還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒吃得這麼飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我想著如果慢慢吃應該能吃完的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間也差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要關門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然待了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對  是今天的主菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到  還不可以把手拿開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把手拿開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家飯店的露天座位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然冬天不開放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我硬請他們為我們開放的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有街燈…用望遠鏡的話應該能看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從大犬座的腳延伸出去  靠近地平線的紅色星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老人星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(330,435)}Canopus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還擔心如果看不到怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我還是第一次看到真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心你哦  感覺你在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也不怎麼有不勉強也沒關係的應試學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也不用承受過重的壓力連飯也吃不下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:09:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路萬同學的話  只要放鬆一些  注意身體的話就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  趁著還不冷的時候回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間也不早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  近江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼對我這麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…想要我來說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  在這之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到春天之後…再慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮完全…落山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影班在營地周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適當的移動位置是可以的  不過不要離開太遠拍攝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡在天文臺裡繼續錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的最後一天  各自完成成果的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:02.83,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}多麼肯花錢  一人一臺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於攝影部的協助  儘可能借多來了相機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣拼命加油的話好感度就會up了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  我現在就給大家做甜酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白冬天如果冷的話  就能看到這麼多星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城市中就只能看到明亮的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某種意義上來說星座也比較容易連起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種能看得蠻清楚的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵戶座的一等星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(280,435)}Orion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色的參宿四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(351,435)}Betelgeuse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小犬座的南河三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(361,435)}Procyon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大犬座的天狼星連成的冬季大三角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(300,435)}Sirius
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後獵戶座的參宿七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(300,435)}Orion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(381,435)}Rigel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金牛座的畢宿五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(361,435)}Aldebaran
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御夫座的五車二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(360,435)}Capella
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上雙子座的北河三就組成了冬季的大六角形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(280,435)}Pollux
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為已經看慣了…原來是完全不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為冬天有7顆一等星  所以很好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}木乃伊型睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星確實很明亮  空氣感覺也不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空好像更暗一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是錯覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天太陽落山早  所以首先沒有太陽殘照的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且空氣乾燥  透明度更高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天  在城市裡時常能看到清晰得令人驚訝的閃亮星星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明亮的星星  黑暗的天幕  高透明度的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如此  才能看到這清晰的光輝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過像今天這樣的日子有點不適合用望遠鏡看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明閃爍得這麼亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  這樣星光閃爍的夜晚上空的氣流不安定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的閃爍  和透明度沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會因為大氣的晃動而影響成像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如晃動的水面不容易看清水底一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不晃動的話就能看得很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在天文臺裡做影片攝影也是因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅氣流起伏搖曳也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能把視野好的圖像挑選出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此還是要看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  冬天能通過雙筒或者小口徑望遠鏡看到很多有趣的散開星團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個晚上都會很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  小朔  昴宿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從奧利安追逐亂逃的美女姐妹好萌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(218,435)}Orion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  接下來向M35出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M35
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的來源是萌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之我也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's星景拍攝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這個要這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:57.13,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞吞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為平時都是交給江戶川弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的  別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個三腳架再放低點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快門鋼絲頂針放這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.56,0:14:09.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有帶懷爐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷爐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是一次性的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把用桐灰的懷爐放在相機這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣鏡片就不會有水霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戶外用品店就有得賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an9}準備完善的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}懷爐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.20,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an7}結\N實\N的\N三\N腳\N架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  來休息一下怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝甜酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小酒井做的甜酒  今年也是最後一次喝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的是最好喝的  小酒井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說小酒井你還不結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭  不要說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐們就要離開了  好不真實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有學姐們的話  我還能帶動大家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好  你聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果是你們大家的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著高見女子高校的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的覺得大家都各得其樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.06,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(100,100,\alpha&H00&)}之{\r}{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(200,200,\alpha&H00&)}類{\r}{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(300,300,\alpha&H00&)}的{\r}{\alpha&HFF&}{\t(400,400,\alpha&H00&)}…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以杏同學就按你自己的做法做一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說我們自己比較需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有望遠鏡  沒有新生入部的話就會變成同好會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個部不知明年還存不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是  雖然不知道你在不安些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我知道杏同學很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相沢也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  別讓人這麼痛切嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小星見  有什麼想看的天體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  還沒有看過土星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然視野還有點不好  要試試看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我記得上次他們好像說想用自己的望遠鏡來看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是什麼  目鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西也很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有目鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這到處貼滿的標籤是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星  那該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎  我們還一起在上面亂畫過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體  在事故的時候已經壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有目鏡能帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帶些東西跟大家一起分享
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是土星  因為也是爸爸喜歡的天體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起看我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和獅子座恰好重合的就是土星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗七星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大角星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(320,435)}Arcturus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角宿一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(320,435)}Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起看過的春天的星星也開始可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空轉了一圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星與星連結起來季節的接力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又開始新一輪的接力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  也試試導入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come come  朔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡和這裡調動一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡  不是這裡？ 這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名流了好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入畫面了就調整焦距
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣  看的到光環嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多虧了目鏡的關係嗎  很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然視野一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是搖搖曳曳小小的映像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小  不過好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有光環
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟伽利略號的圖一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(289,435)}Galileo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這宇宙感是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白大家為什麼想看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離太陽第六近的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少人親眼看過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把這份感動像這樣傳遞才有了現在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也  想傳遞下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小星見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要在春天到來的時候  在新的地方把這份感動傳遞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  或許我還不夠可靠  不過我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  多虧了你  今天很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼榮的各位也謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給下一次輪回的星星  鳴禮炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極樂極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿果然少不了這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音…你們的稿子有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  有在好好寫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年開始就是二年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為文藝部員要更加好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來學姐  那是竹筒敲石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的天空之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這許多接力傳遞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.69,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.07,0:22:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為新生馬上就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不引人注目一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此你也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路萬部長考上了大學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天開始要和近江學姐一起過校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們各自都升了一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校裡也來了新生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後天文部為了存續問題努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部員最少也要拉一個進來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承路萬部長  我被任命為部長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明野美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要竭盡全力出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜學姐來當應該比較好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最熱情的可是美星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  拉一個人沒什麼難的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  江戶川  認真一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經被分到別的班級去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連社團活動也沒了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  我跟你不是一個班了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我們是天文部三人組了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到隔壁班去找你玩可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的一句話我就能夠好好努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小朔  那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…雖然去年有時也發一些壁報
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想今年應該更努力一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創刊號加上募集部員的傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好  這很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來看一下  我們是天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天文部  給
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是天文部…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:23:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想讓你們部存續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜第二次連任會長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.07,0:24:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是浪費  難得能寫出這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚前輩在誇獎文章
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去做你們該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.72,0:24:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我還沒有給你屋頂的使用權啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡星星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.57,0:24:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部正在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部員大大大大大招募中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起來  看星星
