Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}就算一句話也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}說出願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:24:00.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}是實現的 First-step First-sign
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}是你喜歡的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:06.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}自己的答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:11.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an7}向著宇宙（更加地）把謎（華麗地）打上去
